but the people wanted more...

22
00:01:29,339 --> 00:01:31,512
來帶領他們的戰鬥
someone to lead them in battle.

23
00:01:31,592 --> 00:01:33,265
那你們想怎麼樣   一位王
- What do you want? - A king.

24
00:01:33,343 --> 00:01:36,142
