A king? They become tyrants.

25
00:01:36,221 --> 00:01:38,349
由上帝選中的王不會這樣
Not if they are chosen by God.

26
00:01:38,432 --> 00:01:44,735
掃羅  我膏你作以色列的第一位王
Saul, I anoint you the first king of Israel.

27
00:01:44,813 --> 00:01:48,443
我想，作為神的先知
May I, as God's prophet,

28
00:01:48,525 --> 00:01:51,199
我可以盡我所能幫助你
help you in any way I can.

29
00:01:51,278 --> 00:01:56,375
