They're ready.

33
00:02:14,176 --> 00:02:16,349
撒母耳在哪裡
Where is Samuel?

34
00:02:16,428 --> 00:02:18,430
他應該在這裡
He should be here.

35
00:02:19,765 --> 00:02:22,609
我們必須在我們開戰前獻祭
We must make a sacrifice before we attack.

36
00:02:26,313 --> 00:02:28,111
我們不能再等了
We cannot wait any longer.

37
00:02:35,197 --> 00:02:37,291
掃羅  願上帝饒恕你
Saul! May God forgive you!

38
00:02:37,366 --> 00:02:39,039
撒母耳
Samuel.

39
00:02:39,117 --> 00:02:40,585
你在這幾天在哪裡
Where were you?

40
00:02:40,661 --> 00:02:43,915
我們已經等待了七天   七天
Seven days we have waited. Seven days.

41
00:02:43,997 --> 00:02:45,499
