殺滅萬事萬物
kill everyone and everything

47
00:03:14,569 --> 00:03:18,369
在以色列歷史上開始了一個新時代
A new era in Israelite history is beginning...

48
00:03:18,448 --> 00:03:21,702
先知和君王的時代
the period of prophets and kings.

49
00:03:23,537 --> 00:03:27,792
他們必須共同努力，以保護應許之地
They must work together to secure the promised land.

50
00:03:35,174 --> 00:03:37,141
