And who is this pagan king?

63
00:04:43,532 --> 00:04:46,457
過會兒就處死他
He is to be put to death later.

64
00:04:46,535 --> 00:04:49,790
主說寬恕  你便可寬恕
When the Lord says spare, you spare.

65
00:04:49,873 --> 00:04:51,921
