What the Lord gives, he can take away.

69
00:05:04,429 --> 00:05:06,306
這是上帝說的還是你說的
Are these God's words or yours?

70
00:05:06,389 --> 00:05:10,394
你的後裔本可以統治逾千年
Your descendants could have ruled for over a thousand years.

71
00:05:13,021 --> 00:05:15,148
