But today,

72
00:05:15,232 --> 00:05:17,234
上帝已經拋棄你了
God has forsaken you.

73
00:05:17,901 --> 00:05:20,324
上帝還說了什麼
More divine words?

74
00:05:24,574 --> 00:05:27,453
上帝已收回你的能力
God has torn your power from you.

75
00:05:28,912 --> 00:05:31,756
他想找一個合他心意的人
He wants a man after his own heart

76
00:05:51,726 --> 00:05:54,070
給我倒酒  -是的陛下
Bring me wine. Sire.

77
00:05:56,690 --> 00:05:58,784
聽到沒有  快點
Do you hear me? Now!

78
00:05:58,859 --> 00:06:00,361
是  陛下
Yes, sire!

79
00:06:03,280 --> 00:06:05,533
也許是我太不耐煩了
Perhaps I have been hasty.

80
00:06:07,909 --> 00:06:10,537
我應該祈求撒母耳的原諒
I should ask Samuel's forgiveness.

81
00:06:12,122 --> 00:06:15,717
把撒母耳帶來見我
Bring Samuel to me.

82
00:06:15,792 --> 00:06:17,794
他走了  陛下
He's gone, Majesty.

83
00:06:19,337 --> 00:06:20,839
走了
Gone?

84
00:06:25,927 --> 00:06:27,895
撒母耳
Samuel!

85
00:06:47,824 --> 00:06:49,918
掃羅觸怒了上帝
After Saul's disobedience,

86
00:06:49,993 --> 00:06:53,213
