God commands his prophet Samuel...

87
00:06:53,288 --> 00:06:55,382
尋找一位新的王
to find a new king.

88
00:07:10,180 --> 00:07:12,182
年輕人
Young man!

89
00:07:14,351 --> 00:07:16,695
你叫什麼名字
What is your name?

90
00:07:17,270 --> 00:07:18,988
大衛  先生
David, sir.

91
00:07:19,940 --> 00:07:22,193
我叫大衛
My name is David.

92
00:07:42,420 --> 00:07:45,424
我膏立於你  伯利恆的大衛
I anoint you, David of Bethlehem,

93
00:07:45,507 --> 00:07:48,511
在掃羅死後
to be the next king of Israel...

94
00:07:49,844 --> 00:07:51,972
繼任以色列王
once Saul is dead.

95
00:08:01,648 --> 00:08:03,321
父親  怎麼了
Father, what's wrong?

96
00:08:04,985 --> 00:08:06,737
告訴我怎麼了
Tell me what's wrong.

97
00:08:08,363 --> 00:08:09,831
沒事
Nothing is wrong.

98
00:08:09,906 --> 00:08:11,704
這是一場偉大的勝利
It was a great victory.

99
00:08:11,783 --> 00:08:15,754
我需要休息  僅此而已
I need rest. That is all.

100
00:08:17,247 --> 00:08:20,342
睡吧  睡吧
Sleep. Sleep.

101
00:08:20,417 --> 00:08:23,887
主啊  寬恕你的僕人吧
Lord, forgive your servant!

102
00:08:31,177 --> 00:08:32,679
後來
In time,

103
00:08:32,762 --> 00:08:36,016
大衛成了掃羅的朝前侍從
David becomes an attendant in Saul's court...

104
00:08:37,058 --> 00:08:39,436
一位奉侍王室的 預備王儲
a king in waiting.

105
00:08:53,532 --> 00:08:57,333
非利士人的威脅持續增強
The Philistine threat continues to grow.

106
00:09:01,041 --> 00:09:03,794
現在他們有了一個新的勇士
Now they have a new champion...

107
00:09:07,464 --> 00:09:08,966
歌利亞
Goliath.

108
00:09:21,144 --> 00:09:23,363
你們誰敢出來與我作戰
Will one of you fight me?

109
00:09:23,438 --> 00:09:26,942
以色列人  你們贏了
Israelites, you win,

110
00:09:27,025 --> 00:09:30,495
非利士人就做你們的奴隸
and the Philistines will be your slaves.

