Where is your god?

125
00:10:17,367 --> 00:10:18,869
我會殺了他
I will kill him.

126
00:10:19,994 --> 00:10:21,712
帶上這個
You'll need this.

127
00:10:34,259 --> 00:10:36,353
沒有這個更好
I'll be better without it.

128
00:10:41,724 --> 00:10:45,900
我雖然行過死陰的幽谷
Yea, though I walk in the valley of the shadow of death,

129
00:10:47,230 --> 00:10:48,948
也不怕遭害
I fear no evil...

130
00:10:49,816 --> 00:10:51,864
只因你與我同在
for you are with me.

131
00:10:51,943 --> 00:10:53,445
你的杖  你的竿
Thy rod and staff,

132
00:10:54,821 --> 00:10:56,573
都安慰我
they comfort me.

133
00:10:57,574 --> 00:10:59,622
你用油膏了我的頭
You anoint my head with oil.

134
00:11:01,119 --> 00:11:02,712
使我的福杯滿溢
My cup over?ows.

135
00:11:03,872 --> 00:11:06,625
我一生一世必有恩惠慈愛
Surely goodness and mercy shall follow me...

136
00:11:07,667 --> 00:11:09,761
隨著我
all the days of my life.

137
00:11:33,026 --> 00:11:35,245
看來以色列找到一位勇士了
Israel has found a champion.

138
00:11:44,495 --> 00:11:46,793
別浪費我時間  小伙子
Don't waste my time, little boy.

139
00:11:46,872 --> 00:11:48,921
你現在死還太年輕了
You're too young to die.

140
00:11:52,045 --> 00:11:54,093
我要和你戰鬥
I will fight you.

141
00:12:25,078 --> 00:12:28,332
父親  他成功了  大衛成功了
Father, he did it. David did it.

142
00:12:42,136 --> 00:12:45,140
去抓奴隸吧
Let us make slaves of them!

143
00:12:55,191 --> 00:12:56,443
大衛
David!

144
00:12:57,360 --> 00:12:59,613
勇猛的牧羊英雄
My wolf in shepherd's clothing.

145
00:12:59,696 --> 00:13:02,950
你挽救了我的王國  牧羊人勇士
You've saved my kingdom, my shepherd warrior!

146
00:13:03,616 --> 00:13:05,243
跟我來  兄弟
Come with me, brother.

147
00:13:16,421 --> 00:13:19,391
大衛加入了掃羅的軍隊
David joins Saul's army...

148
00:13:19,465 --> 00:13:22,139
與非利士人打了幾十年的仗
and battles the Philistines for decades.

149
00:13:32,270 --> 00:13:34,068
