You hear that, Father?

159
00:14:02,425 --> 00:14:04,052
我聽到了
I hear.

160
00:14:04,135 --> 00:14:05,853
掃羅  掃羅
Saul! Saul!

161
00:14:05,928 --> 00:14:09,523
掃羅  掃羅  掃羅
Saul! Saul! Saul!

162
00:14:11,059 --> 00:14:14,029
