He'll want my crown next.

168
00:14:28,868 --> 00:14:33,920
大衛  大衛
David! David!

169
00:14:41,255 --> 00:14:43,223
我以為你當時摔下馬了
I thought you were going to fall off your horse.

170
00:14:43,299 --> 00:14:44,972
是摔下了馬
I did fall off my horse.

171
00:14:45,051 --> 00:14:47,053
我摔下來的時候還壓死了一個人
I think I killed a man when I landed on him.

172
00:14:47,136 --> 00:14:49,764
