And yet still it seems it is not enough.

246
00:22:28,222 --> 00:22:29,815
永遠不夠
Not enough.

247
00:22:29,891 --> 00:22:32,233
上帝與我同在
God is with me!

248
00:22:32,309 --> 00:22:34,277
上帝與我同在
God is with me!

249
00:22:37,982 --> 00:22:39,780
主啊
Lord!

250
00:22:42,444 --> 00:22:46,119
您聽見你的僕人嗎？
Do you hear your servant?

