那你為何沒有下手
Why didn't you take it then?

257
00:23:57,102 --> 00:23:59,446
主自會懲罰你對我犯下的罪孽
The Lord may revenge the harm you have done to me,

258
00:23:59,521 --> 00:24:01,523
但惡事出於惡人
but only evildoers do evil deeds.

259
00:24:01,607 --> 00:24:04,406
我卻不加害於你
So my hand will not touch you. Ever.

260
00:24:04,485 --> 00:24:08,034
可是上帝會賞賜你  你將成為王
And God will reward you,and you will be king!

261
00:24:08,155 --> 00:24:10,328
您才是我的王   輪到你當王了   
You are my king. And when you have my crown,

262
00:24:10,407 --> 00:24:13,160
