will you not kill my descendants, bury my name?

263
00:24:13,285 --> 00:24:14,628
我不會   不會嗎
I will not. No?

264
00:24:14,703 --> 00:24:16,546
我發誓
I swear.

265
00:24:18,040 --> 00:24:19,542
不會嗎
No?

266
00:24:20,542 --> 00:24:21,919
那你過來
Come then.

267
00:24:22,879 --> 00:24:24,095
過來
Come.

268
00:24:25,255 --> 00:24:27,054
我們一起回家
We'll go home together.

269
00:24:51,906 --> 00:24:54,911
你當時為何不趁機殺了他
Why did you not kill him when you had the chance?

270
00:24:56,996 --> 00:24:59,044
因為他也是受膏者之一
Because he's one of the anointed.

271
00:25:01,209 --> 00:25:04,087
唯有上帝才能決定他的命運
It's up to God to decide his destiny.

272
00:25:07,215 --> 00:25:08,716
父親
Father!

273
00:25:09,717 --> 00:25:10,718
父親
Father!

274
00:25:10,801 --> 00:25:11,893
父親
Father.

275
00:25:13,012 --> 00:25:14,434
父親
Father.

276
00:25:14,513 --> 00:25:18,359
非利士軍隊駐扎在基利波附近的山谷
The Philistine army is in the next valley, near Gilboa.

277
00:25:18,434 --> 00:25:21,984
約拿單  大衛可能會暗算我們
Jonathan, David is very near.

278
00:25:22,062 --> 00:25:24,941
別再想大衛了
Forget about David.

279
00:25:26,275 --> 00:25:28,369
你必須保衛自己的王國
You must defend your kingdom.

280
00:25:28,444 --> 00:25:30,617
這是你的職責
That is your duty.

281
