是否因我罪孽深重
Were my sins so great...

296
00:27:14,883 --> 00:27:16,885
所以整個以色列都要受苦受難
all of Israel must suffer?

297
00:27:58,385 --> 00:27:59,853
駕  駕
Hyah! Hyah!

298
00:28:15,777 --> 00:28:17,404
非利士人
A crushing victory...

299
00:28:19,323 --> 00:28:20,950
大獲全勝
for the Philistines.

300
00:28:27,956 --> 00:28:29,458
掃羅呢
And Saul?

301
00:28:32,879 --> 00:28:35,301
死了
Dead.

302
00:28:40,052 --> 00:28:43,272
你認為上帝的受膏者身亡不值一提嗎
You think the death of God's anointed is a trivial thing?

303
00:28:44,806 --> 00:28:46,649
約拿單呢
What of Jonathan?

304
00:28:48,685 --> 00:28:50,608
被俘了嗎
Captured?

305
00:28:54,441 --> 00:28:55,943
殺了他
Get rid of him!

306
00:29:10,374 --> 00:29:12,547
一代偉人竟這般逝去
How are the mighty fallen.

307
00:29:21,843 --> 00:29:23,641
我們可以回家
We can go home.

308
00:29:29,227 --> 00:29:31,604
現在人民只能指望你了
The people will look to you now...

309
00:29:31,687 --> 00:29:34,315
抵御外敵  凝聚人心
to defend them, unite them.

310
00:29:39,861 --> 00:29:41,738
是時候了
Our time has come.

311
00:29:47,369 --> 00:29:49,588
是的  我的陛下
Yes, my king.

312
00:29:59,047 --> 00:30:00,845
大衛王
King David.

313
00:30:03,135 --> 00:30:05,433
大衛召集了追隨者
David gathers followers.

314
00:30:05,512 --> 00:30:09,562
但想團結以色列百姓  還需城池來建都
But to unite Israel, he needs a capital city.

315
00:30:10,267 --> 00:30:11,940
耶路撒冷
Jerusalem.

316
00:30:12,019 --> 00:30:13,862
我們的新家園
Our new home.

317
00:30:16,231 --> 00:30:18,233
