Now we just need to find a way in.

318
00:30:19,192 --> 00:30:21,115
如何進城
How do we do that?

319
00:30:22,279 --> 00:30:23,906
只有一個法子
There is one way.

320
00:30:24,906 --> 00:30:27,785
等待夜幕的降臨
We wait till nightfall.

321
00:31:27,761 --> 00:31:29,763
現在怎麼辦
What do we do now?

322
