Uriah!

327
00:33:36,932 --> 00:33:39,151
以色列
Israel!

328
00:34:01,581 --> 00:34:05,631
耶路撒冷城現在是大衛的都城了
Jerusalem is now David's city,

329
00:34:05,710 --> 00:34:08,805
這座城市成為以色列人新的權力中心
a new center of power for the Israelites...

330
00:34:10,173 --> 00:34:14,178
也是他們信仰上帝的終極象徵
and a home for the ultimate symbol of their bond with God.

331
00:34:14,261 --> 00:34:16,559
約櫃
The Ark of the Covenant!

332
00:34:31,861 --> 00:34:34,205
我的朋友  你妻子太漂亮了
Your wife's far too pretty for you, my friend.

333
00:34:34,322 --> 00:34:35,665
沒錯
You're right.

334
00:34:35,782 --> 00:34:37,500
陛下   來
Majesty. Come.

335
00:34:37,617 --> 00:34:40,166
你不介意吧  烏利亞  -可我介意
You don't mind, Uriah. I mind.

336
00:35:33,173 --> 00:35:35,551
如今上帝才真正與我同在了
Now God is truly with me.

337
00:36:11,002 --> 00:36:12,720
陛下
Your Majesty.

338
00:36:13,213 --> 00:36:15,261
先知
Ah. Prophet.

339
00:36:20,595 --> 00:36:22,097
看
Look.

340
00:36:22,180 --> 00:36:24,353
這是我獻給
My temple.

341
00:36:24,432 --> 00:36:25,809
約櫃的聖殿
For the Ark.

342
00:36:25,892 --> 00:36:27,519
也獻給主
For the Lord.

343
00:36:27,602 --> 00:36:29,650
這會是世上獨一無二的聖殿
The world's never seen anything like it.

344
00:36:29,729 --> 00:36:31,777
主昨晚降臨
The Lord came to me last night.

345
00:36:31,856 --> 00:36:33,779
