387
00:39:54,142 --> 00:39:57,066
可我的士兵們還駐扎在野外
While my men are camped in open country,

388
00:39:57,145 --> 00:39:59,193
與敵人激戰
fighting the enemy?

389
00:40:00,315 --> 00:40:02,534
這是一場聖戰
This is a holy war.

390
00:40:02,609 --> 00:40:06,705
我怎麼可以回家  與妻子共度良宵
How could I go to my home and spend the night with my wife?

391
00:40:06,779 --> 00:40:09,373
所以你這麼受人愛戴  烏利亞
That does you credit, Uriah.

392
00:40:09,449 --> 00:40:11,451
但是說實在的
But, man to man,

393
00:40:11,534 --> 00:40:13,036
誰會知道這事
who's to know?

394
00:40:14,787 --> 00:40:16,505
我自己心知肚明
I will know.

395
00:40:20,835 --> 00:40:22,462
正直之士啊
Good man.

396
00:40:23,588 --> 00:40:25,306
讓我們開懷暢飲吧
Then let's drink.

397
00:40:26,674 --> 00:40:28,096
上酒
Wine!

398
00:40:46,736 --> 00:40:50,366
大衛無法迫使烏利亞與拔示巴同床
David cannot force Uriah to sleep with Bathsheba.

399
00:40:52,200 --> 00:40:54,953
所以他另覓他法
So he finds another way...

400
00:40:55,036 --> 00:40:57,164
來掩蓋通奸之事
to conceal his adultery.

401
00:41:17,350 --> 00:41:20,729
約押將軍  我命令你派遣烏利亞
Commander Joab,I order you to send Uriah...

402
00:41:20,812 --> 00:41:22,985
去到陣勢極險之處
to where the fighting is fiercest...

403
00:41:23,064 --> 00:41:25,817
丟下他  令其自生自滅
and abandon him there to die.

404
00:41:55,263 --> 00:41:57,265
我們真是福澤深厚
We've been richly blessed.

405
00:41:59,392 --> 00:42:02,145
你以為可以掩蓋自己所做的事嗎
You think you can just sweep what you've done under the carpet?

406
00:42:03,521 --> 00:42:06,866
你奪走了你最忠誠的僕人烏利亞的一切
You took everything from your most loyal servant, Uriah.

407
00:42:06,983 --> 00:42:09,452
你本該敬重他才是  -我確實尊重他
He deserved your respect. I did respect him.

408
00:42:09,527 --> 00:42:10,949
是嗎
Really?

409
00:42:11,070 --> 00:42:13,869
你奪人妻子  然後又害死了他   先知
You took his wife, then you took his life. Prophet!

410
00:42:13,947 --> 00:42:16,952
你以為上帝對此一無所知嗎
You think God doesn't see everything?

411
00:42:18,786 --> 00:42:20,788
上帝已經對我說了
The Lord has spoken to me.

412
00:42:20,872 --> 00:42:23,842
由於你蔑視上帝
He will bring disaster on your house...

413
00:42:23,916 --> 00:42:26,465
他將讓你一家蒙受災難
for the contempt you have shown the Lord.

414
00:42:33,342 --> 00:42:35,686
不  -不
- No. - No!

415
00:42:35,762 --> 00:42:37,981
他將拿去你的兒子
He will take your son.

416
00:42:42,226 --> 00:42:43,694
我們走著瞧
We shall see.

417
00:42:59,535 --> 00:43:01,879
主啊  我願奉獻一切
Anything, Lord.

418
00:43:03,288 --> 00:43:05,508
請饒過吾兒吧
Please spare my child.

419
00:43:10,379 --> 00:43:12,006
請告訴我
Tell me.

420
00:43:14,509 --> 00:43:16,682
告訴我該做什麼
Tell me what to do.

421
00:43:26,646 --> 00:43:27,897
哦
Oh.

422
00:43:31,692 --> 00:43:35,196
先是我丈夫  現在是我的孩子
First my husband, now my son.

423
00:43:37,198 --> 00:43:38,871
我們被咒詛了
We are cursed.

424
00:43:41,536 --> 00:43:43,459
但我是受膏者
But I was anointed.

425
00:43:44,789 --> 00:43:46,336
上帝賜福於我
God blessed me.

426
00:43:46,415 --> 00:43:48,383
王永遠不可能超越上帝
A king is never above his god.

427
00:43:49,710 --> 00:43:51,963
你本應以祂之名治理國家  而不是為你一己私欲
You were supposed to rule in his name, not your own.

428
00:43:52,046 --> 00:43:53,764
我們完了
We're finished.

429
00:43:54,841 --> 00:43:57,435
所有人都會看出  上帝已經拋棄了我們
Everyone will see that God has left us.

430
00:44:04,976 --> 00:44:06,569
先知
Prophet.

431
00:44:07,895 --> 00:44:11,616
雖然你意志薄弱  他依然愛你  大衛
Even though you are weak, he loves you, David.

432
00:44:13,067 --> 00:44:16,241
你在人間建立了上帝的國度
You have forged God's nation on earth.

433
00:44:19,490 --> 00:44:21,492
相互慰藉吧
Take comfort in each other.

434
00:44:22,660 --> 00:44:24,662
你們還會有兒子的
You will have another son.

435
00:44:44,640 --> 00:44:46,483
小心  所羅門
Be careful, Solomon.

436
00:44:46,559 --> 00:44:47,731
讓他玩吧
Let him play.

437
00:44:48,561 --> 00:44:50,404
這是聖殿
It's the house of the Lord.

438
00:44:51,981 --> 00:44:54,279
總有一天  他要建立聖殿
One day, he'll have to build it.

439
00:44:55,985 --> 00:44:59,285
所羅門會建造聖殿
Solomon will build God's temple.

440
00:44:59,363 --> 00:45:01,206
但如他父親一般
But like his father,

441
00:45:01,281 --> 00:45:05,128
他會發現  遵守上帝的誡命難於登天
he will find it impossible to obey God's commandments.

442
00:45:07,663 --> 00:45:09,916
下集《聖經》預告
Next time on The Bible.

443
00:45:09,999 --> 00:45:11,592
尼布甲尼撒  尼布甲尼撒
Nebuchadnezzar! Nebuchadnezzar!

444
00:45:11,667 --> 00:45:14,762
上帝將從巴比倫帶來災難
God is bringing disaster from Babylon!

445
00:45:14,837 --> 00:45:16,339
尼布甲尼撒
Nebuchadnezzar!

446
00:45:16,422 --> 00:45:17,924
我們前進
We move!

447
00:45:18,007 --> 00:45:19,884
耶路撒冷
Jerusalem!

448
00:45:26,015 --> 00:45:29,861
你不向上帝傳達我們需要幫助嗎
Will you not speak for us in our hour of need?

449
00:45:30,978 --> 00:45:32,525
看看外面
Look out there.

450
00:45:33,397 --> 00:45:35,320
為時已晚
You're too late.

451
00:45:36,359 --> 00:45:38,111
戰爭開始了
It begins.

452
00:45:40,112 --> 00:45:44,117
臣服於尼布甲尼撒王   向他跪拜
Submit to King Nebuchadnezzar. Bow your head.

453
00:45:52,375 --> 00:45:55,845
不管耶路撒冷還剩下什麼   隨你們處置
And whatever is left of Jerusalem, help yourselves!

454
00:45:57,797 --> 00:46:00,016
這邊走  但以理
This way, Daniel.

455
00:46:09,100 --> 00:46:11,148
我們還會回到耶路撒冷嗎
Will we ever return to Jerusalem?

456
00:46:11,227 --> 00:46:13,571
耶利米保證過... 終有一天我們會的
Jeremiah promised that one day we would.

457
00:46:13,646 --> 00:46:15,740
到那時  我們該怎麼做
In the meantime, what do we do...

458
00:46:15,815 --> 00:46:17,783
對這個暴君俯首稱臣嗎
just bow our heads and serve this monster?

459
00:46:17,858 --> 00:46:20,407
我會讓他們臣服的
I will make them bow.

460
00:46:20,486 --> 00:46:21,954
給我點火
Bring me fire!

461
00:46:22,029 --> 00:46:24,498
耶和華  救我
Lord! Save me!

462
00:46:32,790 --> 00:46:35,964
如果預言是正確的  那麼古列會釋放我們
Cyrus will set us free if the prophecy is right.

463
00:46:36,043 --> 00:46:37,545
我不能言而無信
I cannot go back on my word.

464
00:46:37,628 --> 00:46:39,881
我已承諾人民信仰自由
I promised them freedom to worship.

465
00:46:39,964 --> 00:46:41,841
這只是考驗他們的忠誠而已
It is merely a test of their loyalty.

466
00:46:41,924 --> 00:46:44,302
這是個圈套  他們想置我們於死地
It's a trap for all of us. They want us dead.

467
00:46:47,513 --> 00:46:50,858
將來的那一位  他將用火來施洗
There is one to come who will baptise with fire.

468
00:46:50,933 --> 00:46:53,607
我不過是曠野中的吶喊   做好準備    迎接
I'm just a voice in the wilderness,preparing the way for the...

469
00:46:56,271 --> 00:46:57,443
主
Lord.

470
00:46:57,523 --> 00:46:59,901
我們要做什麼
What are we gonna do?

471
00:46:59,984 --> 00:47:01,531
改變世界
Change the world.

